Title: Programmable Automation Laboratory at USC
Body: Date: Wednesday, 20-Nov-96 20:07:03 GMT Server: NCSA/1.3 MIME-version: 1.0 Content-type: text/html Last-modified: Friday, 12-Jul-96 23:22:19 GMT Content-length: 3236 Programmable Automation Laboratory at USC Programmable Automation Laboratory Headed by Prof. Ari Requicha , the lab conducts research on Computational Geometry, Robotics and Artificial Intelligence, with emphasis on their applications in intelligent systems for electromechanical design and manufacturing.
